{"tid":302550,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽晚會出去嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2017-06-29T12:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T03:07:02.000Z","uid":33880,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d376d9a3f2ae54f77c273729e08677d729ed0da4","tid":302550,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T12:54:04.000Z","msg":"幾樣嘢提提大家<br />\n無論係第一次參加獨派集會定係經常發夢嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\n出去前:<br />\n1.搭車用散銀 八達通就不了 最好坐巴士小巴<br />\n2.帶個口罩傍身<br />\n3.可以嘅 盡量着啲方便活動嘅衫<br />\n4.個人資料（中英文全名，身份證號碼）交比可以信任嘅朋友 叫佢有咩事搵唔到你 交你資料比星火或者月光<br />\n<br />\n到尖咀:<br />\n1.好大機會有好多狗 會查身份證 會查袋 但係記得 <span style=\"color: red;\">狗係無權開鎖你部電話</span><br />\n2.可以嘅 搵多兩三個朋友一齊行 <br />\n3.單拖嘅 自己小心啲 去到睇下有無人可以一齊行<br />\n<br />\n有突發:<br />\n1.無心理準備嘅 盡早離開現場 散銀搭車走<br />\n2.運動員 唔洗多講 遊擊 唔好死<br />\n<br />\n聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d525f28834c8e2288bf0d98a7d5cc201b22a5c8","tid":302550,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T12:57:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2015/03/08/101298/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2015%2F03%2F08%2F101298%2F&d=A7hDTDjdZBMZZ4aiadAEC26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b9bf8937\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2015/03/08/101298/</a><br />\n<br />\n當時光復嘅一篇須知 作為獨派 你一定要知"},{"pid":"7b7559b4f65e12a906ac29718b4b60b81d3f030a","tid":302550,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T12:59:19.000Z","msg":"政事台無乜人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"196f4760b8c8229e3d3f25fa7450a2a881f9899e","tid":302550,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89521e15934a6e2694242cd8885aa91877ce305","tid":302550,"uid":16462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T13:03:11